Welcome to SnapVault

The Ultimate Secure Photo Gallery Platform

SnapVault is not just another cloud photo storage. Its a next-generation platform designed to protect your digital memories with military-grade encryption, intelligent organization, and seamless sharingall under your control.

We combine intuitive design with advanced cybersecurity to deliver a gallery experience thats as safe as it is simple.

{/* What Makes SnapVault Unique */}

What Makes SnapVault Unique?

  • 1. End-to-End Security
    Your photos are encrypted on your device before they ever reach our servers.
    Only youand those you explicitly authorizecan access your content.
    We use AES-256 and TLS 1.3 to keep data secure at all times.
  • 2. Smart Photo Management
    Auto-categorization by date, location, faces, and eventswithout compromising your privacy.
    Search your gallery with powerful filters, not AI models trained on your content.
  • 3. Private Sharing, Redefined
    Share albums securely with expiring links, password-protection, and view/download tracking.
    Revoke access at any time.
  • 4. Cloud Convenience with Local Options
    Access your gallery from any device.
    Choose to store backups on your device, private cloud, or encrypted drives.
  • 5. No Ads. No Tracking. Ever.
    We are privacy-first, not ad-driven.
    No facial recognition sent to third parties.
    No hidden analytics. Just full transparency.
{/* Who Is SnapVault For */}

Who Is SnapVault For?

  • Families & Everyday Users
    Preserve and protect your memories across generations.
  • Professional Photographers
    Deliver secure client albums with watermarking and download control.
  • Enterprises & Agencies
    Manage sensitive media with granular permissions, audit logs, and access control.
{/* How to Get Started */}

How to Get Started

  1. Create Your Free Account: Get started in seconds with just an email. No credit card required.
  2. Upload & Organize: Import photos from your device, Google Photos, Dropbox, or directly via drag-and-drop.
  3. Secure & Share: Create albums, apply security controls, and share with peace of mind.
{/* Privacy Commitment */}

Your Privacy Is Our Priority

Were committed to digital freedom. With SnapVault:

  • You own your photos.
  • You control who sees them.
  • You decide how long they stay.
  • No third parties. No fine print. No compromises.

Welcome to SnapVault

SnapVault is a smart, AI-powered resume fraud detection tool designed to help organizations and recruiters verify the authenticity of candidate resumes with speed and accuracy. Whether it's fabricated work history, exaggerated achievements, or fake certifications, SnapVault spots inconsistencies before they become costly mistakes.

{/* Why SnapVault Section */}

Why SnapVault?

In today's competitive hiring landscape, resume fraud is on the rise. SnapVault leverages advanced algorithms and pattern analysis to detect anomalies in submitted resumes. Our platform is intuitive, secure, and tailored for HR professionals, educational institutions, and background verification agencies.

{/* What We Offer Section */}

What We Offer

Instant Resume Scanning

Fraud Detection Reports

Secure Document Handling

Resume Analytics

AI-Powered Analysis

{/* How It Works Section */}

How It Works

AI Analysis

Get Results

Detailed fraud detection report

Simply upload a resume and let SnapVault handle the verification. Our engine cross-checks qualifications, employment history, and other details against known data sets and credibility markers. Within seconds, get a full fraud detection report and risk score.
